antigovernment workers union where about 1500 construction 
workers were protesting economic measures enacted a week earlier 
also friday jose castillo osejo director of the 
antisandinista radio corporation claimed interior minister tomas 
borge summoned him to his office berated radios reporting of the 
demonstrations and punched him in the mouth 
